<date box="[159,290,793,818]" pageId="19" pageNumber="264" value="1845" valueMax="1924">1845–1924</date>
), it is now in BMNH. It was afterwards illustrated by 
<bibRefCitation author="Houlbert" box="[894,1286,793,818]" pageId="19" pageNumber="264" refString="Houlbert, C. (1918) Revision monographique de la sous-famille des Castniinae. Etudes de Lepidopterologie comparee, 15, i - xvi + 1 - 730, pls. 437 - 462, figs. 1 - 242." type="journal article" year="1918">Houlbert (1918: pl. 456, fig. 3829)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="19.[151,1437,721,1394]" pageId="19" pageNumber="264">
<materialsCitation ID-GBIF-Occurrence="1638471453" country="Peru" county="Caballococha" latitude="-3.9" location="Cavallo-Cocho" longLatPrecision="1307" longitude="-70.51667" municipality="Caballo Cocha" pageId="19" pageNumber="264" specimenCount="1" stateProvince="Amazones" typeStatus="holotype">
